; FOUND by P4 stress harness 2026-07-02 (ledger ESH-0102). RESOLVED 2026-07-04.
;
; MUTUAL tail calls are now proper R7RS tail calls: a call in tail position to
; another function is emitted as LLVM `musttail`, so each ping->pong hop reuses
; the frame and runs in O(1) stack (like self-recursion, rec_tco_1e8.esk 10^8).
;
; History (before the fix, master 2692ca63, macOS arm64, -r and AOT):
;   depth 300000 -> OK; 500000 -> SIGILL; 10^7 -> SIGILL, RSS ~535MB at death.
; After the fix (fix/mutual-tail-tco): 10^7 hops -> "OK ping", RSS ~225MB (-r) /
; ~27MB (AOT), sub-second. This is now a regression guard, not an XKNOWN.
(define (ping n) (if (= n 0) (quote ping) (pong (- n 1))))
(define (pong n) (if (= n 0) (quote pong) (ping (- n 1))))
(display "OK ") (display (ping 10000000)) (newline)
